pdate','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/\" title=\"Rick Spitler\">Rick Spitler</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','We gave a very successful\nProgress review on the market playbooks assignment today April 30','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/',2,0,'2014-04-30 20:13:57',1,0,0,0,NULL),(157,9,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/\" title=\"Rick Spitler\">Rick Spitler</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','meeting with Dan Tuccillo in NYC tomorrow morning for 6 hours.  Discussion is integrated deposit planning, progress on Pricetek loans, interview for market playbook logic, etc.','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/',2,0,'2014-04-30 20:16:59',1,0,0,0,NULL),(158,9,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/\" title=\"Rick Spitler\">Rick Spitler</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Meeting scheduled for May 29th in Pittsburgh with Brent Vanderheide to talk about his functions and our support.\nWe still don\\\'t have the social date with his people scheduled?  Is that right?','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/',2,0,'2014-04-30 20:20:34',1,0,0,0,NULL),(159,10,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/mrice/\" title=\"Michael Rice\">Michael Rice</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Terry Begley (4-15); business is good but working harder as pricing and structures get worse. Worried about commercial deposits and wants to talk about E2E lending process improvement oppt. ','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/mrice/',2,0,'2014-05-01 00:29:30',1,0,0,0,NULL),(160,10,'groups','activity_update',