leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/',2,0,'2014-05-01 13:17:47',1,0,0,0,NULL),(166,9,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/\" title=\"Rick Spitler\">Rick Spitler</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Phone call with Dan Tuccillo Thursday May 1.  Talked about his need to rationalize the analytics supporting the consumer balance sheet view of  the bank\\\'s five year board level planning, annual/budget level planning, official reforecast, quarterly pricing and tactics planning, CCAR submissions, and LCR calculations.   We laid out a matrix of these planning processes (rows) and the various types of analytics (elasticity, behaviorial life, FTP etc.) as columns and suggested that working through the cells of the matrix would allow the bank to assign particular analytics to groups and then coordinate how they come together for different planning purposes.  He will talk to Neil next week.  We are to deliver a version of our matrix.  We are then to get together and think about how to prioritize and what we might do to help him along.','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/',2,0,'2014-05-03 10:36:00',1,0,0,0,NULL),(167,9,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/\" title=\"Rick Spitler\">Rick Spitler</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Spoke with Alistair today.  Introduced Lee to him on the topic of negotiated loan pricing.  He is expecting call from Lee to discuss loan pricing of private banking loans.  He also expects a call from Kevin to brief him on the market playbook work.  Finally, he is interested in understanding what knowledge management approach Lyons may be taking and believes that the private banking world needs to follow suit.  I agreed to send him anything we did on knowledge management for Lyons to him','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/',2,0,'2014-05-06 20:18:21',1,0,0,0,NULL),(170,8,'activity','activity_comment','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/akornberg/\" title=\"Ariel Kornberg\">Ariel Kornberg</a> posted a new activity comment','Testing comments','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/akornberg/',140,140,'2014-05-07 20:32:31',1,2,3,0,NULL),(171,26,'groups','joined_group','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/lkyriacou/\" title=\"Lee Kyriacou\">Lee Kyriacou</a> joined the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/admin/',2,0,'2014-05-08 13:49:40',1,0,0,0,NULL),(172,26,'members','last_activity','','','',0,NULL,'2014-05-15 12:37:53',0,0,0,0,NULL),(173,26,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/lkyriacou/\" title=\"Lee Kyriacou\">Lee Kyriacou</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Followed up w/ e-mail to Alistair -- sent him a PNC commercial loan pricing deck; reached out to his assistant for time to review with Alistair, and to discuss applications to private bank loan negotiation.','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/lkyriacou/',2,0,'2014-05-08 15:39:44',1,0,0,0,NULL),(174,13,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rsolomon/\" title=\"Richard Solomon\">Richard Solomon</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Left a voice mail with Brent V on the comparative analytics / benchmarking','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rsolomon/',2,0,'2014-05-08 20:51:45',1,1,4,0,NULL),(175,13,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rsolomon/\" title=\"Richard Solomon\">Richard Solomon</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Have request to get ICON Lendershare data outstanding with Erol A (on Brent\\\'s team)','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rsolomon/',2,0,'2014-05-08 20:52:13',1,1,4,0,NULL),(176,9,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/\" title=\"Rick Spitler\">Rick Spitler</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','presentation of negotiated loan pricing materials scheduled for Wed May 14','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rspitler/',2,0,'2014-05-13 17:35:19',1,0,0,0,NULL),(177,13,'activity','activity_comment','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rsolomon/\" title=\"Richard Solomon\">Richard Solomon</a> posted a new activity comment','Erol sent back the signed Lendershare Agreement - Janet needs to review prior to getting to Icon','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rsolomon/',175,175,'2014-05-15 02:30:01',1,2,3,0,NULL),(179,10,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/mrice/\" title=\"Michael Rice\">Michael Rice</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','5/8: talked to Chris Ward (Hd of TM Prod Mgt). Business has been good. We discussed both liquidity movement and pricing structure changes. Thinks our approach to modeling the market flows makes sense and would be open to further discussions on pricing. Has one of his guys calling us regarding liquidity training. ','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/mrice/',2,0,'2014-05-15 11:24:29',1,0,0,0,NULL),(180,14,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/ktravis/\" title=\"Kevin Travis\">Kevin Travis</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Talked to Dale Klose and Lou Cestello (co heads of the market presidents). They are concerned about making sure our playbooks findings link with them. It turns out the market presidents have control of the sponsorships and local spend, even though they have no role in retail. We suggested extending the work to their commercial lines. Working on a price, ','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/ktravis/',2,0,'2014-05-15 12:17:56',1,0,0,0,NULL),(181,14,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/ktravis/\" title=\"Kevin Travis\">Kevin Travis</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Matt Steenson, head of mass affluent. Matt called Rick, left a message asking about what segmentation information  will be available for Chicago (ethnic in particular). I am in process following up with him. ','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/ktravis/',2,0,'2014-05-15 12:31:29',1,0,0,0,NULL),(182,26,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/lkyriacou/\" title=\"Lee Kyriacou\">Lee Kyriacou</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Rick and I had a call arranged by Alistair J with the PNCAdvisors Private Bank lending execs -- Walter Welsh (US), Fred Frank (East), Maggie Dempsey (West).  Presented the commercial loan analysis of PNC CIB.  They have a $7B portfolio, the bulk of which is consumer lending categories (largely HELOC and Mtge), and ~$2B investment-secured lines.  They half got the concepts of elasticity and measuring willingness to pay, but didn\\\'t quite see it yet.  We offered to do some on-our-nickel portfolio analysis, and they said they would get back to us.','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/lkyriacou/',2,0,'2014-05-15 12:41:32',1,0,0,0,NULL),(183,13,'activity','activity_comment','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rsolomon/\" title=\"Richard Solomon\">Richard Solomon</a> posted a new activity comment','Got in touch with Brent - he said we should reach out to Robert Boone and he will give Robert a heads up as well.  \nI told Janet who should be reaching back out to Robert on this topic.','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/rsolomon/',174,174,'2014-05-15 23:27:25',1,2,3,0,NULL),(184,14,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/ktravis/\" title=\"Kevin Travis\">Kevin Travis</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Matt Steenson 5-21: Left message and sent email to Matt Steenson re: his segmentation request. Awaiting a reply. ','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/ktravis/',2,0,'2014-05-20 15:33:16',1,0,0,0,NULL),(185,14,'groups','activity_update','<a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/ktravis/\" title=\"Kevin Travis\">Kevin Travis</a> posted an update in the group <a href=\"https://leadtracker.novantas.com/clients/pnc-team/\">PNC</a>','Neil Hall 5-21:  Sent Neil a note, suggesting a meeting with Rick and I to follow up on the playbooks work. \n','https://leadtracker.novantas.com/members/ktravis/',2,0,'2014-05-20 15:34:03',1,0,0,0,NULL);
